      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait hydrogen peroxide?? i dont know about that, seems a bit intense. i feel fine otherwise, just quiet in that ear. do u really think i need a doctor right now? i was thinking maybe i could just try some eardrops from the pharmacy or maybe even some of that olive oil stuff i read about online to see if it helps clear it out? sounds way easier than sitting in an er waiting room for hours.",
